			<h2 class="featurette-heading">Blessings</h2>
			<p>Describing her typical day, Blessings writes "everyday I wake up at 05 hours to sweep our family’s compound, fetch water, prepare food and bath before I walk six kilometers to school. When I arrive home from school I help my family fetch more water, wash plates and prepare for dinner. On the weekends, my family and I spend most of Saturday attending to our fields and Sunday’s at church. 
". When she is not working, Blessings likes dancing with her friends, playing netball and singing in the church choir. Blessings' nominator writes that "Blessings parents are extremely supportive of her going to secondary school and only wish they had the ability to send her themselves.</p>
