			<h2 class="featurette-heading">Gladys</h2>
			<p>"I want to continue school until I finish it all", is an outstanding quote from Gladys' application. She writes in no uncertain terms about her desire to go to secondary school and later to university. Her nominator says that this desire is evident and that Gladys comes to school no matter how bad the weather or any other extenuating circumstances. Gladys' family will not be able to pay for her secondary school education, although both her parents strongly support it.</p>
