			<h2 class="featurette-heading">Kabaso</h2>
			<p>Kabaso is one of ten children, all orphaned last year. Right now, her siblings manage to pay her modest school fees, but those will increase dramatically when she enters Grade 10, making it impossible for her to continue without support. Her aunt and uncle have agreed to help Kabaso pay for a uniform, etc. if accepted into a secondary school but cannot provide more. Kabaso is particularly interested in technology, and would like to be a teacher.</p>
